{"sections":{"image_text_UzaarW":{"type":"image-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/omiSky-Reflex-Motion-Interactive-Ceiling-Mirror-Image-Projection-System-3.jpg","image_position":"second","title":"Transform Any Space with OM Interactive Projectors ","text":"<p>Create inclusive, multi-sensory environments that inspire active engagement through motion. Perfect for homes, schools, hospitals, and hospices, these interactive projectors empower users to influence and interact with their surroundings through movement, exploration, and collaboration. <\/p><p><strong>Why Choose OM Interactive?<\/strong> <\/p><ul><li><strong>Calming or Stimulating Sensory Spaces:<\/strong> Immerse users in serene environments like relaxing water effects to promote calm or stimulate the senses. Able to control levels of stimulation. <\/li><li><strong>Dynamic Learning Experiences:<\/strong> Spark curiosity with interactive themes such as outer space, fostering a love for discovery and learning. <\/li><li><strong>Skill Development:<\/strong> Enhance cause-and-effect understanding, social interaction, motor skills, critical thinking, and organizational abilities. <\/li><li><strong>Engaging Activities:<\/strong> A variety of captivating options like <em>Wipe<\/em>, <em>Splat<\/em>, <em>Water<\/em>, <em>Quiz<\/em>, <em>Zones<\/em>, and <em>Scatter<\/em> ensure every session is enjoyable and stimulating.  <\/li><li><strong>Easy to Use:<\/strong> Intuitive design makes setup and operation effortless, suitable for all abilities and ages. <\/li><\/ul><p>Whether you’re creating a calming retreat or an interactive learning environment, OM Interactive projectors provide endless possibilities for meaningful, engaging experiences.<\/p>","link":"","link_label":"","padding_top_desktop":30,"padding_bottom_desktop":30,"padding_top_mobile":20,"padding_bottom_mobile":20}},"custom_liquid_V3DbmA":{"type":"custom-liquid","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<section class=\"hero-banner\">\n  <div class=\"he